           move      spaces               to   w-sta-dis-ecc-e05      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Per causale della scadenza nr. 2            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-sta-dis-ecc-e06      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
