           move      rf-sfp-abi-pgf       to   w-sta-dis-ecc-c01      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Denominazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-axi-den    to   w-sta-dis-ecc-d01      .
       pre-are-wcc-200.
