      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Denominazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-axs-loc    to   w-sta-dis-ecc-l03      .
       pre-are-wcc-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
